<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 23 日星期二 18:04:28 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Israel Boasts of 'Ability to Hit Iran' as Nuclear Tensions Seethe]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110543950" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/17/1110543793_0:0:700:467_1440x900_80_0_1_72b1ec91902f83950d3941c45c50d071.jpg?source-sid=" data-photoview-image-id="1110543775" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/israel-boasts-of-ability-to-hit-iran-as-nuclear-tensions-seethe-1110543950.html?share-img=1110543775"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"><span class="photoview__copyright"></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">以色列国防军总参谋长 Herzi Halevi 在 2023 年 5 月 23 日于以色列举行的一次安全会议上讨论了伊朗所谓的威胁，以及以色列攻击该国的能力。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="" alt="Israel Defense Forces Chief of General Staff Herzi Halevi discusses the alleged threats posed by Iran, and Israel's capabilities to attack the country, at a security conference in Israel on May 23, 2023. - Sputnik International, 1920, 23.05.2023" title="以色列国防军总参谋长 Herzi Halevi 在 2023 年 5 月 23 日于以色列举行的一次安全会议上讨论了伊朗所谓的威胁，以及以色列攻击该国的能力。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/17/1110543793_0:37:700:431_1920x0_80_0_0_fa583db9cafd902c06ea2247c7a2ab7c.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/17/1110543793_0:37:700:431_640x0_80_0_0_ced8f77f448edecbcb688a6769ccbc16.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/17/1110543793_0:37:700:431_1280x0_80_0_0_d57c1df2f27ac4fa410ffff3b352c7bb.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/17/1110543793_0:37:700:431_1920x0_80_0_0_fa583db9cafd902c06ea2247c7a2ab7c.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">特拉维夫十多年来一直指责德黑兰追求核武器。伊斯兰共和国一直否认这些说法，并呼吁国际社会更加关注以色列，暗示这个犹太国家拥有自己的核武器储备。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">以色列国防军总参谋长 Herzi Halevi 宣布，如果德黑兰核计划出现“负面发展”，以色列准备对伊朗实施打击，并敦促向以色列国防军拨款，以进一步提高特拉维夫的军事能力。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">哈勒维周二在以色列荷兹利亚举行的安全会议上<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hiUeFgmfg9E" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">说</a>：“无需详细说明，地平线上可能会出现可能促使采取行动的负面事态发展。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “伊朗在铀浓缩方面取得的进展比以往任何时候都多。我们也在密切研究核能力之路的其他方面，”这位指挥官说，并警告德黑兰“我们有能力，其他国家也有能力”，以色列有“打击伊朗的能力。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110543950" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/israel-boasts-of-ability-to-hit-iran-as-nuclear-tensions-seethe-1110543950.html?share-block=1110543953" data-title="&amp;quot;Iran has made more progress in uranium enrichment than ever before. We are also closely examining other aspects of the way to nuclear capability,&amp;quot; the commander said, warning Tehran that &amp;quot;we have abilities and others have abilities,&amp;quot; and that Israel has &amp;quot;the ability to hit Iran.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">哈勒维认为以色列目前准备攻击德黑兰的军事潜力是“良好的”，但建议进一步“加强”它们，以便特拉维夫“能够对伊朗进行广泛的战役”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">哈勒维承认，以色列国防军面临许多阻碍其对抗伊朗能力的障碍，并指出该国距离以色列超过 1,500 公里，这使其成为以色列空军具有挑战性的目标。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “以色列国防军的建立是为了在我们的后院进行战争。我们没有远征军，这不符合我们的军事文化，我们必须培养这些能力。伊朗很大——是以色列的 70 倍。当它部署它的时候整个领域的能力，我们需要知道事情在哪里才能伤害这个巨大地理领域的每一点。这是一个与我们以前面临的不同的挑战。伊朗也有很多人口——是以色列人口的十倍。它有一个大经济体......在一个衡量标准上他们接近我们在不同的衡量标准上它似乎更大一些。但是第五个重要的数字是我们的机会：以色列的人均产品几乎是伊朗人均产品的四倍经济，这是我们的机会，因为这是质量，”指挥官说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110543950" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/israel-boasts-of-ability-to-hit-iran-as-nuclear-tensions-seethe-1110543950.html?share-block=1110545125" data-title="&quot;The IDF was built to conduct warfare in our backyard. We don't have expeditionary forces, it's not in our military culture, and we must build those abilities. Iran is big – it's 70 times the size of Israel. When it deploys its ability all over this domain we need to know where things are to be able to hurt every point on this huge geographical domain. It's a different challenge than we faced before. Iran also has a big population – ten times the population of Israel. It has a big economy…On one measurement they are close to us on a different measurement it seems a bit bigger. But the fifth number that is important is our opportunity: the product per capita of Israel is almost four times the per capita product of the Iranian economy, which is our opportunity because this is quality,&quot; the commander said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在评论伊朗与包括地区重量级沙特阿拉伯在内的其他海湾国家之间的外交和解趋势时，哈勒维对其战略意义置之不理。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “在过去几个月里，我们周围的一些国家出现了与伊朗和解的现象。但我不认为这是这些国家尊重伊朗或信任它或希望与它达成和平协议的结果......我相信这是他们希望降低周围环境温度而不引发任何冲突的结果——这是他们的选择，”他说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">仇敌</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">自 1979 年伊朗革命推翻了该国美国支持的独裁者以来，以色列和伊朗一直是死敌，并在德黑兰成立了拒绝承认以色列存在权的伊斯兰共和国政府。多年来，两国一直在多条战线上进行激烈的秘密战争，包括长期的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220319/alleged-iranian-hackers-reportedly-release-new-info-on-mossad-chief-1094013864.html" target="_blank">网络战</a>、 <a href="https://www.jpost.com/breaking-news/article-743868" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">隐蔽的海战</a>以及<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230409/explosions-reported-around-damascus-as-idf-strikes-syria-1109283928.html" target="_blank">叙利亚</a>和<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220823/hezbollahs-victory-in-1985-2000-war-shattered-idfs-air-of-invincibility-nasrallah-says-1099913026.html" target="_blank">黎巴嫩</a>的代理人冲突。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">特拉维夫指责德黑兰试图制造核弹。德黑兰保留在其和平核能计划下继续其铀浓缩活动的权利，并一再强调它没有寻求核武器和任何种类的大规模杀伤性武器的计划。相反，这个伊斯兰共和国依靠庞大的常规弹道导弹和巡航导弹以及无人机作为其对侵略的主要威慑力量。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伊朗向国际原子能机构和联合国安理会提出了一些令人不安的问题，即为什么其和平核活动受到严格的国际监督，而这些机构却对以色列视而不见，以色列被<a href="https://www.sipri.org/media/press-release/2022/global-nuclear-arsenals-are-expected-grow-states-continue-modernize-new-sipri-yearbook-out-now" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">广泛怀疑</a>拥有数十个核武器。特拉维夫不承认其核武器地位，而是奉行“故意含糊其辞”的政策。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">以色列和美国开展了联合训练活动，模拟对伊朗核设施的攻击，特拉维夫特别拨款 15 亿美元，为这种可能发生的情况做准备。然而，一些<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220104/israeli-ex-official-points-to-mammoth-frightening-tool-iran-has-to-answer-attack-on-nuclear-sites-1092017791.html" target="_blank">以色列官员警告说，如果特拉维夫继续攻击伊朗，灾难性后果</a>可能降临在特拉维夫身上。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Tue, 23 May 2023 17:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/israel-boasts-of-ability-to-hit-iran-as-nuclear-tensions-seethe-1110543950.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/israel-boasts-of-ability-to-hit-iran-as-nuclear-tensions-seethe-1110543950.html<category>世界</category><category>以色列</category><category>伊朗</category><category>德黑兰</category><category>以色列国防军 (IDF)</category><category>国际原子能机构 (IAEA)</category><category>特拉维夫</category><category>核</category><category>罢工</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Putin Meets With Republika Srpska Leader Dodik]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110535992" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/17/1110536158_0:0:3144:204